# """
# Fetch YouTube transcripts for videos selected from channels in an Excel registry.

# Selection logic (default):
#   - For each channel: scan newest uploads (scan_recent)
#   - Filter: duration >= min_minutes
#   - Filter: title/description must match at least one keyword (keywords)
#   - Keep top per_channel matches (newest-first)

# Outputs:
#   out_dir/
#     manifest.csv
#     C01_ChannelName/
#       V0001.txt
#       V0001.meta.json
#       ...

# Requirements:
#   pip install google-api-python-client youtube-transcript-api isodate pandas openpyxl
# """

